# VoxBulk VPS (production)

User deploys from a **Linux VPS** (Baota / aaPanel). Treat VPS deploy and git pull issues as first-class when they ask about production.

## Repository on VPS

- **GitHub:** `https://github.com/menasimuk-hub/Vox-new.git` — branch `main`
- **Repo root:** folder containing `deploy-vps.sh`, `vox.sh`, `voxbulk-api/`
- Typical path on server: `/www/voxbulk` or similar (confirm with user if needed)

## Deploy (on VPS — not Windows)

```bash
cd /path/to/Vox
chmod +x deploy-vps.sh vox.sh
./deploy-vps.sh
```

- Prefer **`./deploy-vps.sh`** as the deploy user — **not** `sudo sh ./deploy-vps.sh`
- Script uses `bash`; it calls `sudo` internally for `apt-get` and rsync to wwwroot
- Equivalent: `./vox.sh update`

## Static wwwroot (Baota defaults in deploy-vps.sh)

| App | Build output | wwwroot |
|-----|--------------|---------|
| Admin | `admin.voxbulk.com/adim-web/dist/` | `/www/wwwroot/admin.voxbulk.com` |
| Dashboard | `dashboard.voxbulk.com/dashboard-web/dist/client/` | `/www/wwwroot/dashboard.voxbulk.com` |
| Public site | vite preview :5173 (not static wwwroot by default) | — |

## API

- FastAPI: `127.0.0.1:8000` (uvicorn via `vox.sh`)
- Production API host: `https://api.voxbulk.com`
- Config: `voxbulk-api/.env` (never commit)

## Git pull blocked by untracked brand/logo files

Common after brand assets were synced manually on VPS then added to git:

```
error: The following untracked working tree files would be overwritten by merge:
  admin.voxbulk.com/adim-web/public/brand/*.png
  dashboard.voxbulk.com/dashboard-web/public/brand/*.png
```

**Fix on VPS (safe — only removes untracked copies):**

```bash
cd /path/to/Vox
rm -f admin.voxbulk.com/adim-web/public/brand/icon-black.png \
      admin.voxbulk.com/adim-web/public/brand/icon-white.png \
      admin.voxbulk.com/adim-web/public/brand/logo-black.png \
      admin.voxbulk.com/adim-web/public/brand/logo-white.png \
      dashboard.voxbulk.com/dashboard-web/public/brand/icon-black.png \
      dashboard.voxbulk.com/dashboard-web/public/brand/icon-white.png \
      dashboard.voxbulk.com/dashboard-web/public/brand/logo-black.png \
      dashboard.voxbulk.com/dashboard-web/public/brand/logo-white.png
git pull origin main
./deploy-vps.sh
```

Newer `deploy-vps.sh` runs `_clear_untracked_pull_conflicts` before pull automatically.

## OAuth redirect URIs (production)

- Google/Apple/LinkedIn callback: `https://api.voxbulk.com/auth/oauth/{provider}/callback`
- Configure in Admin → Integrations → Social login **and** the provider console

## Vite preview host check (nginx → :5173)

If the public site shows **Blocked request. This host ("voxbulk.com") is not allowed**, ensure `voxbulk.com/frontend/vite.config.ts` has `preview.allowedHosts` including `voxbulk.com` and `www.voxbulk.com`, then rebuild and `./vox.sh restart`.

## Skip flags

```bash
VOX_SKIP_GIT=1 ./deploy-vps.sh
VOX_SKIP_BUILD=1 ./deploy-vps.sh
VOX_SKIP_MIGRATE=1 ./deploy-vps.sh
VOX_FORCE_PULL=1 ./deploy-vps.sh   # stash + retry pull (use with care)
```
